EU citizens are calling for action to improve #FairTaxation.
8 out of 10 respondents of our public consultation believe international tax rules for the digital economy need to change.
Learn more → https://t.co/MS4eZnc7MN #EUHaveYourSay https://t.co/jzkHgfW9nI

We have decided to take the lead and we will encourage our partners to follow → https://t.co/MS4eZnc7MN https://t.co/vXsNNXSCs0

Digital platforms will be deemed to have a taxable 'digital presence' if they fulfil one of the following criteria in a Member State:
📎 +€7 million in annual revenues or,
📎 +100000 users or,
📎 +3000 business contracts for digital services
Learn more → https://t.co/MCLAg3ADHP https://t.co/7VOEjqcRXe

Digital companies currently have an average effective tax rate half that of the traditional economy in the EU

data.text:
Today we fine 8 Asian companies €254 million for operating a global cartel for supply of aluminium and tantalum electrolytic capacitors.
Capacitors are in most electric and electronic products in European households, like TVs, PCs or refrigerators: https://t.co/labCRS1Vm9 https://t.co/9etqEmW4Mw

data.text:
We have approved the Bayer/Monsanto merger on condition that a large part of Bayer's existing businesses be sold to a third party. 
We have also fined 8 companies producing capacitors a total of over €250m for taking part in a cartel @vestager https://t.co/bNV3Kq81lM

On International Day for the Elimination of Racial Discrimination, we reaffirm our commitment to work until discrimination, hatred and violence have no more place anywhere. #IDERD #FightRacism https://t.co/PRacsmtefE

Commissioner @vestager will be in the press room today at +/-11h30 CET to present a merger decision and a cartel decision. 
Follow live on Periscope and EbS → https://t.co/brjnsvrpky https://t.co/hUzZCMVA0n

data.text:
One market – one Europe. 
In 25 years, we've come a long way. Let's keep making the Single Market even stronger.
Ahead of #EUCO @JunckerEU, @EP_President and @EU2018BG reaffirm their support to the EU #SingleMarket → https://t.co/2bqrY5J6lq https://t.co/EEAzmZ0OwU
#InternationalDayofHappiness: Are you happy living in the EU? 78% of Europeans say yes! 🇪🇺 https://t.co/UVvC38J4hI #FutureofEurope https://t.co/zsuUiQtt0g

The European #SingleMarket is 25 years young.
A generation of Europeans has grown up with it. 
We will keep making it stronger so that the next generation will benefit even more.
Our joint statement → https://t.co/2bqrY5J6lq https://t.co/u4m4AtrfCo
